This backend is better to be hosted in fcitx upstream.
Temporarily put it here.

BUILD
=============================
./autogen.sh
./configure --prefix=<xxx>
make
make install

SETUP
============================
add:

export GTK_IM_MODULE=xim
export QT_IM_MODULE=xim
export XMODIFIERS=@im=fcitx
export XIM_PROGRAM=fcitx

to your ~/.bashrc

or you can use im-switch (only available on some distros)

RUN
============================
fcitx


Enjoy ...
